Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.50,0:15:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're actually Nana-chan's classmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.14,0:15:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was surprised as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.31,0:15:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were actually Nana-san's elder brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.01,0:15:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't hold back, so I sent you a letter, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.60,0:16:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.21,0:16:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.09,0:16:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.23,0:16:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.59,0:16:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am getting married.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.75,0:16:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.90,0:16:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My fiancé is the only son of a former financial clique.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.58,0:16:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though it was actually my father's selfish decision...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.93,0:16:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.75,0:16:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. This doesn't have anything to do with you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.88,0:16:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it's already this late...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.21,0:16:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a curfew, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.31,0:16:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, my school has very strict regulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.24,0:16:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll walk you back to the dorms.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.82,0:16:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.87,0:17:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That incident has become the topic of the dorms.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.72,0:17:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, even for such a wealthy ladies' school?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.88,0:17:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.54,0:17:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially for Nana-san, who's all excited about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.53,0:17:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She even went to the crime scene of the incident to do some detective work...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.99,0:17:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should never get involved with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.38,0:17:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't make it in time, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.72,0:17:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.49,0:17:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.83,0:17:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can get in through here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.20,0:17:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nana-san told me about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.66,0:17:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you should reconsider your friendship with Nana-chan for your own sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.20,0:17:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shugo-sama, this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.31,0:18:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.33,0:18:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shugo-sama, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.76,0:18:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're safe now. No one will come in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.41,0:18:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Takako-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.28,0:18:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.32,0:18:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think there's a need for me to come in too...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.18,0:18:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I'll be off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.39,0:18:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takako-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.98,0:18:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.59,0:18:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.51,0:18:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know whether or not I should just abide by my father's orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.78,0:18:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.81,0:18:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takako-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.19,0:18:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the very least, I want to be with you for tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.00,0:18:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please save me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.01,0:18:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please save me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.82,0:18:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yura...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.14,0:18:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shugo-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.88,0:18:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yura!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.42,0:18:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm Takako.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.70,0:19:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.32,0:19:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.70,0:19:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.02,0:19:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels good...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.65,0:19:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.04,0:20:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shugo-sama... Don't do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.51,0:20:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.31,0:20:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shugo-sama's... Is so manly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.00,0:20:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I actually wanted to do this more skillfully...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.54,0:20:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shugo-sama, what should I do to pleasure you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.41,0:20:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.64,0:20:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, can you suck on it deeper?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.24,0:20:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.85,0:21:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I seem to have licked it a little too deeply.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.17,0:21:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this really fine, Takako-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.81,0:21:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.23,0:21:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I can give my virginity to Shugo-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.65,0:21:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.19,0:21:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.33,0:22:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My body... My body is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.35,0:22:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shugo-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.03,0:22:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shugo-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.87,0:22:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something... Something is coming out!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.55,0:22:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.11,0:22:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's embarrassing...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.08,0:23:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing... You're amazing, Takako-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.13,0:23:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.94,0:23:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.98,0:23:51.03,Signboard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frx342\fry0\move(650,88,550,88,0,9033)}Draperies
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.63,0:23:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Rin! About selling yourself... won't you consider it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.28,0:23:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Master! I will be scolded by the landlady.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.49,0:23:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to have a baby with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.74,0:24:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, Master. Please stop doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.12,0:24:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With that body of yours, having any number of babies won't be a problem at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.37,0:24:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Rin-san, known as "Snow White", right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.61,0:24:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Nana-san's teacher...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.01,0:24:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takashiro-sama is waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.02,0:24:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.11,0:24:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.75,0:24:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened, Nee-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.34,0:24:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rin has...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.82,0:24:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rin hasn't returned after going out for a house-visit!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.55,0:24:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.80,0:24:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, where did she go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.13,0:24:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(0,40)}"Bizarre Murder Case: Mysterious Corpse with Unnatural Cause of Death"{世にも不思議な変死体猟奇殺人事件}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.22,0:24:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me... Rin, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.89,0:25:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if Rin was taken away by the murderer, this place is too conspicuous to be the scene of the crime.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.85,0:25:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She must've been murdered somewhere else before being brought here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.24,0:25:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But how did he do it...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.61,0:25:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Moreover, what exactly did those black crow feathers left in the crime scene signify...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.00,0:25:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It couldn't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.23,0:25:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever the case, this place is too...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.09,0:25:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I have to check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.66,0:25:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.26,0:26:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This smell is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.60,0:26:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rin!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.45,0:26:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.74,0:26:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A corpse...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.74,0:26:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way... This is too...!!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.33,0:26:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Where am I...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.39,0:26:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is troublesome...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.02,0:26:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This place is supposed to be restricted to uninvolved people.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.79,0:26:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.95,0:26:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you, an ecclesiastic, doing such horrible things?!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.61,0:27:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That mark is...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.33,0:27:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.13,0:27:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.60,0:27:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.25,0:27:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have injected you with a specially concocted medicine.{added you with}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.35,0:27:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From today on, you will live only to comfort me.{onwards}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.71,0:28:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels good! Really good!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.21,0:28:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.21,0:28:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hold it in anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.09,0:28:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, you shall forever attend to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.95,0:28:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you going to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.85,0:28:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For that, I shall cut your legs-
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.50,0:28:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.15,0:29:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So {\i1}you{\i0} did this, killing Otoha and disemboweling her!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.38,0:29:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is for the sake of "The Rebirth"!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.02,0:29:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.60,0:29:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wait there!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.74,0:29:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rin!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.00,0:29:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The moment I entered the carriage, \NI already knew who the murderer was.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.26,0:29:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A faint smell of blood was left on the carriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.45,0:29:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the evidence of it transporting corpses.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.95,0:29:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, why? To think that such a model citizen could commit serial murder...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.17,0:29:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukamizu's body was infertile. {@QC: impotent, sterile, barren, fruitless, unproductive, infecund, unprolific}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.04,0:29:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She had an endometrial cyst when she was young, so it seems that she had her uterus removed.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.32,0:30:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From that point on, feelings of malediction against young women started to build up in Fukamizu.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.86,0:30:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moreover, she was under the impression that if she ate the uteri of young women,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.17,0:30:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she thought that she would be able to have babies.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.49,0:30:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the ceremony known as "The Rebirth".
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.93,0:30:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although the police seem to have linked all the serial murders to her, I don't think that that's the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.88,0:30:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.57,0:30:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukamizu was a believer of Senri Shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.33,0:30:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It means that the case will continue, Kazuna.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.76,0:30:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
